long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Stack Jump is a fun adventure game where we try to score points by jumping on brick blocks from the right and left.
There are different characters in the game. We start the game by choosing a character. We try to jump on the brick blocks from the right and left with the feeling we choose. Get points as we jump on the blocks. In addition to the points we get, we also get gold. By purchasing new characters with the gold we obtain, we can partner in this adventure for a long time. Jump Over Jump has emerged as an adventure game designed for children's game lovers, as it is fun and challenging.
To swipe Install this extension to play the Stack Jump Game or offline with no additional downloads and no ads. 

You can contact us at support@724fun.com and share your thoughts and problems

After clicking the add the game to chrome button, you can find the game in the extensions section. If you wish, you can visit 724fun.com. If you wish, you can play again and if you want to remove it, you can remove it from the extensions section.
